<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
<title>AI Search Readiness Audit -- {{domain}}</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0b0d12; --panel: #11141b; --panel-2: #161a23;
    --ink: #e7ebf3; --ink-dim: #9aa3b2;
    --accent: #7c5cff; --accent-2: #22d3ee;
    --good: #34d399; --warn: #fbbf24; --bad: #f87171;
    --line: #232838; --radius: 14px;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html, body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--ink); margin: 0; }
  body { font: 15px/1.55 -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif; padding: 40px 24px 80px; }
  .wrap { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; }

  header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; gap: 24px; margin-bottom: 28px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  header h1 { font-size: 28px; margin: 0 0 4px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
  header .meta { color: var(--ink-dim); font-size: 13px; }
  header .brand { font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-dim); text-align: right; }
  header .brand a { color: var(--accent-2); text-decoration: none; }

  /* Hero */
  .hero { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr; gap: 28px; background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 28px; margin-bottom: 20px; align-items: center; }
  @media (max-width: 760px) { .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .gauge-wrap { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
  .gauge { position: relative; width: 200px; height: 200px; }
  .gauge .ring { width: 100%; height: 100%; border-radius: 50%; background: conic-gradient(var(--accent) calc(var(--val, 0) * 3.6deg), var(--panel-2) 0); display: grid; place-items: center; }
  .gauge .ring::before { content: ""; width: 76%; height: 76%; background: var(--panel); border-radius: 50%; position: absolute; }
  .gauge .num { position: relative; font-size: 64px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.03em; line-height: 1; z-index: 1; }
  .gauge .num small { font-size: 18px; color: var(--ink-dim); font-weight: 500; }
  .score-timeline { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0; width: 100%; }
  .tl-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 3px; }
  .tl-item .tl-label { font-size: 9px; color: var(--ink-dim); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; font-weight: 600; }
  .tl-item .tl-val { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 800; }
  .tl-item.past .tl-val { color: var(--ink-dim); }
  .tl-item.now .tl-val { color: var(--accent-2); }
  .tl-item.target .tl-val { color: var(--good); }
  .tl-arrow { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--line); position: relative; margin: 0 6px; top: 4px; }
  .tl-arrow::after { content: ""; position: absolute; right: -4px; top: -3px; border-left: 6px solid var(--line); border-top: 3px solid transparent; border-bottom: 3px solid transparent; }
  .headline-label { font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-dim); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .headline { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.65; margin: 0 0 14px; }
  .headline strong { color: var(--accent-2); }

  /* Dimension chips */
  .dims { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  @media (max-width: 760px) { .dims { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
  .dim { background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 16px 14px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .dim::before { content: ""; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px; background: var(--line); }
  .dim.p-max::before { background: var(--good); }
  .dim.p-good::before { background: var(--accent-2); }
  .dim.p-mid::before  { background: var(--warn); }
  .dim.p-low::before  { background: var(--bad); }
  .dim .name { font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-dim); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; font-weight: 700; }
  .dim .val { font-size: 34px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 8px 0 2px; line-height: 1; color: var(--ink-dim); }
  .dim.p-max .val { color: var(--good); }
  .dim.p-good .val { color: var(--accent-2); }
  .dim.p-mid  .val { color: var(--warn); }
  .dim.p-low  .val { color: var(--bad); }
  .dim .val small { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink-dim); }
  .dim .blocker { font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-dim); margin-top: 8px; line-height: 1.45; }

  /* Cards */
  section.card { background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 22px 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  section.card h2 { font-size: 17px; margin: 0 0 4px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; font-weight: 700; }
  .card-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-dim); margin: 0 0 16px; line-height: 1.5; }

  /* Tables */
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13px; }
  table th { font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-dim); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.07em; font-weight: 700; padding: 8px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); text-align: left; }
  table td { padding: 11px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); vertical-align: top; }
  table tbody tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  table tbody tr:hover td { background: var(--panel-2); }
  table td a { color: var(--accent-2); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
  table td code { font-size: 11px; background: var(--panel-2); padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 4px; white-space: nowrap; }
  .score-cell { font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; }
  .score-cell.warn { color: var(--warn); }
  .score-cell.bad  { color: var(--bad); }
  .score-cell.good { color: var(--good); }
  .url-cell { white-space: nowrap; max-width: 150px; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }
  .h1-cell { color: var(--ink-dim); font-size: 12px; max-width: 120px; }
  .problem-cell { font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-dim); max-width: 160px; }
  .fix-cell { font-size: 12px; max-width: 220px; }
  .num-cell { font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; color: var(--ink-dim); font-size: 12px; }
  .effort-badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 50%; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; }
  .effort-badge.s { background: rgba(52,211,153,0.18); color: var(--good); }
  .effort-badge.m { background: rgba(251,191,36,0.18); color: var(--warn); }
  .effort-badge.l { background: rgba(248,113,113,0.18); color: var(--bad); }
  .pts { font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent-2); font-size: 13px; }

  /* Fixes list */
  .fixes { display: grid; gap: 8px; }
  .fix-group-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; padding: 4px 0 2px; }
  .fix-group-label.quick { color: var(--good); }
  .fix-group-label.strategic { color: var(--warn); }
  .fix-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 26px 1fr auto; gap: 10px; align-items: start; padding: 12px; background: var(--panel-2); border-radius: 10px; }
  .fix-row .rank { font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent); font-size: 15px; padding-top: 1px; }
  .fix-row .fix-text { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.55; }
  .fix-row .fix-meta { font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-dim); white-space: nowrap; text-align: right; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; align-items: flex-end; }
  .pill { display: inline-block; padding: 1px 7px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; }
  .pill.s { background: rgba(52,211,153,0.15); color: var(--good); }
  .pill.m { background: rgba(251,191,36,0.18); color: var(--warn); }
  .pill.l { background: rgba(248,113,113,0.18); color: var(--bad); }

  /* Progress since last audit */
  .progress-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 10px; }
  @media (max-width: 760px) { .progress-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .progress-item { background: var(--panel-2); border-radius: 10px; padding: 14px 16px; }
  .progress-item .pi-label { font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-dim); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; font-weight: 700; }
  .progress-item .pi-val { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; margin-top: 4px; color: var(--good); }
  .progress-item .pi-sub { font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-dim); margin-top: 2px; line-height: 1.4; }

  /* Buckets */
  .bucket-intro { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-dim); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 14px; padding: 14px 16px; background: var(--panel-2); border-radius: 10px; border-left: 3px solid var(--accent); }
  .bucket-intro strong { color: var(--ink); }
  .buckets { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 10px; }
  @media (max-width: 760px) { .buckets { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
  .bucket { background: var(--panel-2); border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px 14px; }
  .bucket .b-num { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1; }
  .bucket .b-label { font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-dim); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.07em; margin-top: 4px; font-weight: 700; }
  .bucket .b-desc { font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-dim); margin-top: 6px; line-height: 1.4; }
  .bucket.strong .b-num { color: var(--good); }
  .bucket.decent .b-num { color: var(--accent-2); }
  .bucket.weak   .b-num { color: var(--warn); }
  .bucket.invisible .b-num { color: var(--bad); }

  /* Artifacts */
  .artifacts { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 8px; }
  @media (max-width: 760px) { .artifacts { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .artifact { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 10px 14px; background: var(--panel-2); border-radius: 10px; font-size: 13px; }
  .artifact .ico { width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 8px; background: var(--accent); display: grid; place-items: center; color: #fff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 11px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .artifact .ico.ready { background: var(--good); color: #000; }
  .artifact code { background: transparent; color: var(--ink-dim); font-size: 11px; display: block; margin-top: 1px; }

  footer { text-align: center; color: var(--ink-dim); font-size: 12px; margin-top: 32px; line-height: 1.8; }
  footer a { color: var(--accent-2); text-decoration: none; }
  footer strong { color: var(--ink); }

  @media print {
    body { padding: 0; }
    .wrap { max-width: none; }
    section.card, .hero, .dim { break-inside: avoid; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

  <header>
    <div>
      <h1>AI Search Readiness Audit</h1>
      <div class="meta">{{domain}} &nbsp;·&nbsp; crawled {{crawl_date}} &nbsp;·&nbsp; {{urls_crawled}} URLs crawled &nbsp;·&nbsp; JS rendering {{js_rendering}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="brand">
      <a href="https://github.com/{{repo_owner}}/ai-search-auditor">ai-search-auditor</a><br>
      Screaming Frog MCP &nbsp;·&nbsp; Claude
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="gauge-wrap">
      <div class="gauge">
        <div class="ring" style="--val:{{site_score}}">
          <div class="num">{{site_score}}<small>/100</small></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="score-timeline">
        <div class="tl-item past">
          <span class="tl-label">Last audit</span>
          <span class="tl-val">{{prev_score}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tl-arrow"></div>
        <div class="tl-item now">
          <span class="tl-label">Today</span>
          <span class="tl-val">{{site_score}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tl-arrow"></div>
        <div class="tl-item target">
          <span class="tl-label">After fixes</span>
          <span class="tl-val">{{expected_post_fix_score}}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="headline-label">Headline finding</div>
      <p class="headline"><strong>{{headline_gap}}</strong> {{headline_consequence}} {{headline_action}}</p>
      <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-dim);">Top-50 most-linked pages average <strong style="color:var(--ink);">{{top50_avg}}/100</strong>.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dims">
    <div class="dim">
      <div class="name">Bot Access</div>
      <div class="val">{{bot_access}}<small>/20</small></div>
      <div class="blocker">{{bot_access_blocker}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="dim">
      <div class="name">Discovery</div>
      <div class="val">{{discovery}}<small>/20</small></div>
      <div class="blocker">{{discovery_blocker}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="dim">
      <div class="name">Structure</div>
      <div class="val">{{structure}}<small>/20</small></div>
      <div class="blocker">{{structure_blocker}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="dim">
      <div class="name">Citability</div>
      <div class="val">{{citability}}<small>/20</small></div>
      <div class="blocker">{{citability_blocker}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="dim">
      <div class="name">Authority</div>
      <div class="val">{{authority}}<small>/20</small></div>
      <div class="blocker">{{authority_blocker}}</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="card">
    <h2>Page-level working plan</h2>
    <p class="card-desc">Top pages below Decent by inlink count. The ones AI crawlers see most. Fix these first.</p>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Page</th>
          <th>H1</th>
          <th>Words</th>
          <th>Score</th>
          <th>Problem</th>
          <th>How to fix</th>
          <th>Effort</th>
          <th>+pts</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>{{working_plan_html}}</tbody>
    </table>
  </section>

  <section class="card">
    <h2>Top 5 site-wide fixes</h2>
    <p class="card-desc">Patterns that repeat across many pages. Fix these once and every page benefits.</p>
    <div class="fixes">{{fixes_html}}</div>
  </section>

  {{progress_html}}

  <section class="card">
    <h2>Page score breakdown</h2>
    <div class="bucket-intro">
      <strong>How this works:</strong> Every page on your site gets a score from 0 to 100. The score measures how likely AI search engines like ChatGPT, Claude, and Perplexity are to cite that page when answering a question. It combines five signals: bot access, discoverability, schema structure, content citability, and authority. Pages below 60 are rarely cited regardless of content quality.
    </div>
    <div class="buckets">
      <div class="bucket strong"><div class="b-num">{{bucket_strong}}</div><div class="b-label">Strong 80-100</div><div class="b-desc">Citation-ready. AI engines find and cite these.</div></div>
      <div class="bucket decent"><div class="b-num">{{bucket_decent}}</div><div class="b-label">Decent 60-79</div><div class="b-desc">Minor gaps. A few fixes push these into Strong.</div></div>
      <div class="bucket weak"><div class="b-num">{{bucket_weak}}</div><div class="b-label">Weak 40-59</div><div class="b-desc">Structural problems. Needs schema or content rewrite.</div></div>
      <div class="bucket invisible"><div class="b-num">{{bucket_invisible}}</div><div class="b-label">Invisible 0-39</div><div class="b-desc">AI engines skip these entirely.</div></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="card">
    <h2>Generated artifacts</h2>
    <p class="card-desc">Files ready to deploy or hand off to a developer today.</p>
    <div class="artifacts">{{artifacts_html}}</div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    Re-audit in 4 weeks after shipping the top fixes. Expected score: <strong>{{expected_post_fix_score}}/100</strong>.<br>
    Rubric: <a href="https://github.com/{{repo_owner}}/ai-search-auditor/blob/main/.claude/skills/ai-search-audit/rubric.md">deterministic, auditable</a> &nbsp;·&nbsp; v{{rubric_version}}
    <br style="margin-bottom:6px;">
    <span style="font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-dim);max-width:700px;display:inline-block;margin-top:8px;line-height:1.5;">
      Scope: optimized for citations in ChatGPT, Claude, and Perplexity.
      For Google AI Overviews, <a href="https://developers.google.com/search/docs/fundamentals/ai-optimization-guide" style="color:var(--ink-dim);">Google's own guidance</a> prioritizes foundational SEO over llms.txt and structured data -- use Search Console for Google AI signals.
    </span>
  </footer>

</div>
<script>
(function() {
  document.querySelectorAll('.dim').forEach(function(el) {
    var val = parseInt(el.querySelector('.val').textContent, 10);
    var pct = val / 20;
    if (pct >= 1)        el.classList.add('p-max');
    else if (pct >= 0.7) el.classList.add('p-good');
    else if (pct >= 0.4) el.classList.add('p-mid');
    else                 el.classList.add('p-low');
  });
})();
</script>
</body>
</html>
